<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79e99a7d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s4203"><num value="4203">§ 4203.</num><heading> Statement of policy</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">It is the policy of the United States—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id79e99a7e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s4203/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> to assist in the conservation and protection of the African elephant by supporting the conservation programs of African countries and the CITES Secretariat; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id79e99a7f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s4203/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> to provide financial resources for those programs.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id79e99a80-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/478/tII/s2004">Pub. L. 100–478, title II, § 2004</ref>, <date date="1988-10-07">Oct. 7, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2316">102 Stat. 2316</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
